reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Fine, but tight and short.
reviews.reviewText: Got this to use in my car. I liked the idea that it was coiled and not flopping all over the dashboard. This one came in the mail and fairly quickly. It's kinda short and the coil is tight. So I can put my phone close to the charger, but it won't allow me to move the phone around much. Maybe it will loosen up with us. The durability seems good - I just bought this. We will see. Big hopes for a small cord in the future.
